- Begins with O (origin/open/zero) 



- Derived from existing symbolic family 



- Foundational sound 



- Circular phonetics fit zero 



- Visually consistent with SOSAONE

**Semantic interpretation:**

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
